Class SubRealmObserver

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.identity.entitlement.opensso.SubRealmObserver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SetupListener, ServiceListener

    public class SubRealmObserver
extends Object
implements ServiceListener, SetupListener
    This observer will remove all referral and application privileges that have reference to a deleted sub realm.
